{"tid":370818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懶理10號波照落水　市民勸：唔好搞嘢喎","createTime":"2017-08-23T08:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:09:20.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05bafe66f413fb50a0726b8575f412630f484583","tid":370818,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"颱風「天鴿」襲港造成多處破壞，但有人無視十號風球，到海邊觀浪甚至落水嬉戲，有市民大聲勸阻「細佬你唔好搞嘢喎，走呀喂！」，惟觀浪發燒友不為所動。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/08/20170823_CR_%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8_%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF_%E8%A7%80%E6%B5%AA_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F08%2F20170823_CR_%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8_%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF_%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%25B5%25AA_1.jpg&h=e1a4b2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n從疑似大浪灣海邊片段可見，有人在沙灘上觀浪、甚至落水，當巨浪湧至，一度跌倒。有目睹市民大聲勸阻「細佬你唔好搞嘢喎，走呀喂！」，巨浪隨即湧至，觀浪發燒友亦不為所動。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/08/20170823_CR_%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8_%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF_%E8%A7%80%E6%B5%AA_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F08%2F20170823_CR_%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8_%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF_%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%25B5%25AA_2.jpg&h=6f2bb52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n片段被放上網，不少人認為在10號風球下仍堅持滑浪是「玩命」，並稱「有事唔好打999」，更稱「到頭來有咩依郁，就盞連累救護員冒生命危險去救佢！救唔到就賴人哋唔周到、無能之類推卸責任唔會認為自己唔啱嗰囉！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/08/20170823_CR_%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8_%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF_%E8%A7%80%E6%B5%AA_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F08%2F20170823_CR_%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8_%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF_%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%25B5%25AA_3.jpg&h=a381b5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n天文台今早表示，橫瀾島、大老山及長洲泳灘一度錄得最高持續風速，為每小時141、135及126公里，最高陣風分別為每小時192、187及163公里。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/08/20170823_CR_%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8_%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF_%E8%A7%80%E6%B5%AA_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F08%2F20170823_CR_%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8_%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF_%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%25B5%25AA_4.jpg&h=a944bca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://lb01-626056081.ap-southeast-1.elb.amazonaws.com/macau/16-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B/765836-%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E6%87%B6%E7%90%8610%E8%99%9F%E6%B3%A2%E7%85%A7%E8%90%BD%E6%B0%B4-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%B8%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E6%90%9E%E5%98%A2%E5%96%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flb01-626056081.ap-southeast-1.elb.amazonaws.com%2Fmacau%2F16-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B%2F765836-%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B4%25BF%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2587%25B6%25E7%2590%258610%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258B%25B8%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2598%25A2%25E5%2596%258E&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4d6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=4d626dfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://lb01-626056081.ap-southeast-1.elb.amazonaws.com/macau/16-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B/765836-%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A9%E9%B4%BF%E8%A5%B2%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%91%E6%87%B6%E7%90%8610%E8%99%9F%E6%B3%A2%E7%85%A7%E8%90%BD%E6%B0%B4-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8B%B8%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E6%90%9E%E5%98%A2%E5%96%8E</a>"},{"pid":"7dd2fea7387722156ea74491de8b90f811e49e98","tid":370818,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"廢老廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}